    "description": "Carry your passion for gold prospecting or gold panning wherever you go, with our Gold Panner or Sluice Box Stainless Steel Carabiner Keychains.&nbsp;<br><br>Designed for outdoor enthusiasts and hobbyists, these keychains feature detailed, prospecting-inspired silhouettes that reflect the tools and lifestyle of real gold seekers. Whether you’re in the field or just want a subtle nod to your favorite outdoor hobby, these designs bring character to your everyday carry.<br><br>Made from durable stainless steel, each keychain is built to handle rugged environments without rusting or wearing down, meaning they’ll stand up to use around water, dirt and changing outdoor conditions. The solid construction ensures long-lasting performance, whether clipped to your gear during a day at the river or used daily with your keys.<br><br>The integrated carabiner allows for quick and secure attachment to gear, belt loops, keys, backpacks or bags, giving you easy access. The included split ring keeps your keys organized and firmly in place, making it a practical addition to your everyday carry setup or outdoor kit.<br><br><strong>Choose from two styles: Gold Panner or Sluice Box</strong>",
